{"tid":847340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊冪遭中國官媒點名 狠批「演戲完全不過腦子」","createTime":"2018-10-04T05:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T08:46:29.000Z","uid":75969,"like":554,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"d1507b75a4b0dfb1029eef8a870fc98172ed6604","tid":847340,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"〔記者吳孟倫／台北報導〕中國女星楊冪長相甜美，主演過多部知名電視劇，她在新電影《寶貝兒》中有突破性的演出，本被看好能角逐金馬影后，可惜最後還是落馬。不過楊冪的演技一直備受爭議，日前還遭有黨媒色彩的《北京日報》批評。<br />\n<br />\n《北京日報》專欄以「藝術片不是鍍金片」為題，表示楊冪為中國最具商業價值的女星之一，但她的演技卻與知名度成反比，從童星出道的楊冪拍片經驗豐富，演戲對她來說是習以為常的事，因此她都下意識的做出程序化表演，形容她「快樂就是哈哈哈，痛苦就是哇哇哇」，完全不經大腦思考。專欄也提到許多人認為文藝片容易鍍金，但事實卻非如此，並說楊冪在《寶貝兒》中演技進步不大，狠批「同片的其他演員，一個表情、一個眼神都能襯托她在表演上的無力」。<br />\n<br />\n專欄作者也以王安石的《傷仲永》提醒楊冪，表示表演雖需天賦，但這種天賦也要時時磨練，否則只會「泯然眾人矣」。網友們看了表示「這文寫得又狠又準」、「分析可說相當到位了」、「楊冪真該好好提升一下演技了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/10/02/phpgnDWyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2FphpgnDWyX.jpg&h=3674fe77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">楊冪。（翻攝自楊冪微博）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/10/02/phph9Z1C6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2Fphph9Z1C6.jpg&h=07e0fbfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飯冰冰已經玩嫌 有請下一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2568329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2568329&d=Di3Hi8q1XW4ODRW9VD87TcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ef0fa294\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2568329&h=cffb8eb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2568329</a>"},{"pid":"e3fec16bd86ee89f87e095524729537210d80ef5","tid":847340,"uid":128014,"like":365,"dislike":2,"score":363,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等一下</span></span>"},{"pid":"0cd4465a88765f7798e27fd6fcd928b03fa941eb","tid":847340,"uid":134864,"like":490,"dislike":6,"score":484,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"等一下...<br />\n我有老公....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d979783102a30ca20442877e5473dda216c93a","tid":847340,"uid":21545,"like":123,"dislike":54,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"不要 我有老公的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465596cec853d64a8b771b9074439d3275ddaafb","tid":847340,"uid":76310,"like":225,"dislike":2,"score":223,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"呢個好撚有錢<br />\n<br />\n唔斬番筆點叫公平"},{"pid":"fb3fb34324cb45370dbc11b0f9bd18ce91cef425","tid":847340,"uid":210031,"like":76,"dislike":5,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"有老公架人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4d0beef2342352bbfa582b0bb847ea6a939312","tid":847340,"uid":60655,"like":76,"dislike":4,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:56:46.000Z","msg":"郭襄無慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f84f1f13137f90018de9d2e924d94b04955a0db","tid":847340,"uid":39855,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:57:28.000Z","msg":"閒閒地 1000億不是夢，咁多明星。"},{"pid":"c72511f213ff1f8729456fb8f929d976e6beddcd","tid":847340,"uid":37528,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"捉番去調教下囉"},{"pid":"39fc70422522407af5f4244d458a95186998da0f","tid":847340,"uid":8858,"like":255,"dislike":1,"score":254,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:58:58.000Z",